---
import Heading from "../components/ui/Heading.astro"
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"

const lastUpdated = "June 2026"
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now"
  description="What Yash is focused on right now."
>
  <Heading level="h2" as="h1" class="mt-6 mb-2">Now</Heading>
  <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mb-6">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">
      This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">now page</a>.
      It tells you what I am focused on at this point in my life.
    </p>

    <div>
      <Heading level="h3" as="h2" class="mb-3">Building</Heading>
      <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-4">
        <li>
          <a href="https://mumsmemories.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mum's Memories</a>,
          a minimal baby journaling app. I am building it for my own use and
          getting it ready for a wider release.
        </li>
        <li>
          Vidhya AI, a platform to help students prepare for the UPSC exam.
          It has a mobile app, a web app, and a backend API in one repository.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <Heading level="h3" as="h2" class="mb-3">Homelab</Heading>
      <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-4">
        <li>
          I run a homelab with a Raspberry Pi, an OCI VM, and an old HP laptop
          that runs Arch Linux.
        </li>
        <li>
          I plan to connect these machines into a single cluster to run services
          and experiment with distributed systems at small scale.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <Heading level="h3" as="h2" class="mb-3">Work</Heading>
      <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-4">
        <li>
          I was promoted to Staff Software Engineer at Netskope in April 2026.
        </li>
        <li>
          I lead technical work on the CASB API product. We build tools that
          help companies protect their data stored in cloud apps.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <Heading level="h3" as="h2" class="mb-3">Learning</Heading>
      <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-4">
        <li>
          <a href="https://themlbook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Hundred-Page Machine Learning Book</a> by Andriy Burkov
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://anilananthaswamy.com/why-machines-learn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Why Machines Learn</a> by Anil Ananthaswamy
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://tanmoychak.com/llmbook/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Introduction to Large Language Models</a> by Tanmoy Chakraborty
        </li>
        <li>
          I am learning AI engineering by building products on the side.
        </li>
        <li>
          I might take the NPTEL course on
          <a href="https://nptel.ac.in/courses/106102576" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Introduction to Large Language Models</a>,
          but I have not decided yet.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
